description.narrative: Sustainable, positive change for poor and marginalised people and strengthened social accountability

Thirteen NGOS are supported through the programme grant cycle as follows Concern, Trocaire, Gorta-Self Help Africa, Christian Aid Ireland, Oxfam Ireland, Sightsavers, World Vision Ireland, Plan Irelan, ActionAid Ireland, Vita, HElpAge International and Children in Crossfire.
